  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Chalet Blanc is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning a hearty continental breakfast buffet is served between 8-10am.</p>
<p>A three course dinner is served each day, featuring local cuisine and mountain specialties. Served between 7-9:30pm.</p>
<p>The kitchen team emphasis the importance of using local products - many of the items are sourced from the B<span>riançon region.</span></p>
<p>Christmas Eve and New Years' Eve gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
