  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Chalet Blanc is located at the foot of the slopes and with a ski lift opposite it allows superb access to the slopes. Having been renovated in recent years there is a contemporary feel to this traditional hotel. </p>
<h2>Warm and welcoming</h2>
<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
<div class="elementor-row">
<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5b19e797" data-id="5b19e797" data-element_type="column" data-settings="{&quot;_ob_bbad_is_stalker&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_teleporter_use&quot;:false,&quot;_ob_column_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_column_has_pseudo&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}">
<div class="elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated">
<div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-15453782-87af-496f-86cf-00dca42b0cb6ed ob-has-background-overlay elementor-widget elementor-widget-html" data-id="15453782-87af-496f-86cf-00dca42b0cb6ed" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_poopart_use&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}" data-widget_type="html.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p id="text-accueil-icon-1">The hotel was completely renovated in 2021, creating a luxurious and elegant property in the centre of <span><a data-udi="umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606}" title="Montgenèvre">Montgenèvre</a>. Traditional wooden features combined with textiles inspired by nature </span><span>create a welcoming charm, and modern features mean you have all the comforts needed for a week in the Alps. Most of the rooms have a balcony with lovely views of the surrounding alpine scenery, as well as Wi-Fi, and </span><span id="more4">environmentally friendly toiletries including solid shampoo.<br /></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Idyllic location</h2>
<p>With a fantastic location in <span><a data-udi="umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4355b275387942f08b2416ccd4bee606}" title="Montgenèvre">Montgenèvre</a>,  you have easy and convenient access to the slopes of the <a data-udi="umb://document/ac18b1d87c81457eaf0af66a3b8f0b19" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ac18b1d87c81457eaf0af66a3b8f0b19}" title="Milky Way Ski Area">Milky Way Ski Area. </a>The mountain panorama surrounds the hotel so you can enjoy the fabulous views from the comfort of your hotel room or from the sun terrace. </span></p>
<h2>Bar and restaurant</h2>
<p>The lounge and bar are the perfect place to finish a day of skiing, with tapas available alongside signature cocktails and wines. These can also be enjoyed on the sunny terrace which has views over the mountains.</p>
<p>Every day, your plates are filled with delicious market produce, local and high-quality items from the Briançon region. You can appreciate the local cuisine knowing that it has been sourced locally and frequently includes dishes from the region. The mountain specialties and cheeses pair wonderfully with the hotel's cellar selection of wines.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the slopes of the Milky Way, the complimentary relaxation area is the best place to relax. Admire the views of the Alps, and relax in the hammam, sauna and a whirlpool bath are at your disposal in an immaculate environment reminiscent of the magnificent scenery of the Hautes Alpes in winter. The relaxation area is accessible by reservation only.</p>
<p>The Spa is open from 10am to 9pm from early December to mid-April and from late June to mid-September. It is possible to open it during the off-season for groups.</p>]]></description>
