  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong><span> Chalvet </span>Classic Bedrooms</strong> can sleep two people and are around 18m² with a North facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Chalvet Suites</strong> can sleep two to five people and are around 30m². These duplex style suites have two bedrooms, an additional single sofa bed for the fifth person and a North facing balcony.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>USB sockets</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Fridge</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathroom with bath or shower</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Slippers and bathrobes</li>
<li>All bedrooms have a twin or double bed (please specify when booking)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
